    <div class="why-choose-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-between align-items-center">
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h2 class="section-title">Why Choose Us</h2>
            <p>
              At Men's Hub, we prioritize quality, style, and customer
              satisfaction. Our handpicked collections are designed for modern
              men who value both fashion and comfort. With fast shipping, easy
              returns, and excellent support, shopping with us is always a
              seamless experience!.
            </p>

            <div class="row my-5">
              <div class="col-6 col-md-6">
                <div class="feature">
                  <div class="icon">
                    <img src="images/truck.svg" alt="Image" class="imf-fluid" />
                  </div>
                  <h3>Fast &amp; Free Shipping</h3>
                  <p>
                    Enjoy free shipping on all orders at Men's Hub! We ensure
                    your favorite styles arrive quickly and hassle-free. Shop
                    now an d experience fast delivery straight to your door!
