                  <h3>Easy to Shop</h3>
                  <p>
                    Shopping at Men's Hub is a breeze! Our user-friendly website
                    allows you to browse, filter, and find your perfect styles
                    effortlessly. Enjoy a seamless shopping experience from
                    start to finish!
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="col-6 col-md-6">
                <div class="feature">
                  <div class="icon">
                    <img
                      src="images/support.svg"
                      alt="Image"
                      class="imf-fluid"
                    />
                  </div>
                  <h3>24/7 Support</h3>
                  <p>
                    At Men's Hub, we're here for you around the clock! Our
                    dedicated support team is available 24/7 to answer your
                    questions and assist with any issues. Shop with confidence
                    knowing help is just a click away!
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="col-6 col-md-6">
                <div class="feature">
                  <div class="icon">
                    <img
                      src="images/return.svg"
                      alt="Image"
                      class="imf-fluid"
                    />
                  </div>
                  <h3>Hassle Free Returns</h3>
                  <p>
                    At Men's Hub, we believe in making your shopping experience
                    stress-free. If you're not completely satisfied with your
                    purchase, our hassle-free return policy allows you to return
                    items easily and quickly. Shop with confidence, knowing you
                    can return what doesn't work for you!
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
